snippet.title: AMMO NYC DLC - OFFICIAL RELEASE DATE | Steam
snippet.description:
AMMO NYC DLC will be released on - APRIL 13, 2022

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1802260/Car_Detailing_Simulator__AMMO_NYC_DLC/

YES! It's coming next month! 🥳 Together with the release of the full version of the game, you will be able to purchase the AMMO NYC DLC by Larry Kosilly!
